title: New: The Money War – Stars
body:
There’s a real Beatles vibe to the songwriting here from Perth duo **The Money War**.

Lifted from an EP out at the beginning of April, _Stars_ is slick and straight to the point – with an air of romantic wistfulness to it, all-in-all suggesting that The Money War are a force to be reckoned with.
